Body: Description: Error Message " Your appliance is on critical low disk space, there is only 8.78 gb free available from 257.22 gb (3%). Use Audit Log Backup to reduce the logs stored in the database, delete older system and audit log backups, and tune policies to reduce incoming log count. For further assistance contact support.
